flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Receive text task<br/>+ skills directory"]
    B --> C[Scan skills directory<br/>for .md files]
    C --> D[Extract keywords<br/>from each skill file]
    D --> E[Match task against<br/>skill keywords]
    E --> F{Match found?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Select best-fit<br/>skill file]
    F -->|No| H[Use default<br/>skill / fallback]
    G --> I[Load skill Markdown<br/>as prompt template]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Inject task into<br/>skill template]
    J --> K[Send prompt to LLM]
    K --> L[Receive LLM response]
    L --> M([End])